desc_short	-----								Have you always dreamed of making a game but have no wish to delve into the mystical realms of programming or 3D art creation? GameGuru allows you to fulfil your dreams in a non-technical, fun and extremely easy to share way. Create games that you can play and enjoy with others in minutes.							
